The paper discusses an interface for eliciting people's preferences for visual stimuli, which is related to human-computer interaction (cs.HC) and information retrieval (cs.IR). The paper also mentions collecting dense recommender datasets, which falls under machine learning (cs.LG) and computer vision (cs.CV). Lastly, the paper aims to integrate research in recommender systems with social and behavioral sciences, which is related to social and information sciences (cs.SI).
